        <section class="gem-c-notice gem-c-notice--bottom-margin" aria-label="Notice" role="region">
      <span class="gem-c-notice__title">This consultation has concluded</span>


      

  </section>



      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Detail of outcome</h2>

      <div class="consultation-outcome-detail">
        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>A <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/consultations/windrush-compensation-scheme">public consultation on the design of the compensation scheme</a> is now open. We want to hear from those who have been affected by this situation, and their families, on the design of the compensation scheme.</p>
</div>
</div>

      </div>


      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Detail of feedback received</h2>

      <div class="consultation-feedback">
        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The analysis of public feedback is available to read in chapter 2 of the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/consultations/windrush-compensation-scheme">Windrush compensation consultation document</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>

      </div>

      <section class="original-consultation">
        <header>
          <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="original-consultation-title">Original consultation</h2>

        </header>


    <section class="app-c-banner app-c-banner--grid" aria-label="Notice">
      <h2 class="app-c-banner__title">Summary</h2>
  <p class="app-c-banner__desc">
          This call for evidence closed on 8 June 2018 and was the first step to designing a scheme that provides redress for those that have experienced hardship.

  </p>

    <p class="app-c-banner__desc">        This consultation ran from<br></br><span class="consultation-date"><time datetime="2018-05-10T00:00:00.000+01:00">10 May 2018</time> to
        <time datetime="2018-06-08T23:45:00.000+01:00">11:45pm on 8 June 2018</time></span>
</p>
</section>


      </section>


    <div class="consultation-description">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Consultation description</h2>

      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Prime Minister and the Home Secretary have made a pledge to support those of the Windrush generation who have faced difficulties in establishing their status under the immigration system. They have committed to do right by those who have contributed so much and are such an integral part of the country.</p>

<p>A call for evidence was the first step to listen to those affected, before engaging on the details of the scheme. While the 4-week call for evidence to help shape the compensation scheme has closed, individuals can still share their opinions by emailing <a href="mailto:windrushcompensation@homeoffice.gsi.gov.uk">windrushcompensation@homeoffice.gsi.gov.uk</a>.</p>

<div class="call-to-action">
<p>A <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/consultations/windrush-compensation-scheme">public consultation on the design of the compensation scheme</a> is now open. We want to hear from those who have been affected by this situation, and their families, on the design of the compensation scheme.</p>
</div>

<p>We will be announcing details of the final scheme and how to apply as soon as possible after the public consultation has ended.</p>
</div>
</div>


